    {
      "id": "mythical_creature_dragon_wyvern_serpent",
      "name": "Dragon/Wyvern/Serpent",
      "tableCategory": "Mythical Creature",
      "description": "Miniature dragon 9–12 ft (2.7–3.7 m) snout-to-tail; wingspan often exceeds body length. Scaly hide, talons, crocodilian teeth; can fly. No breath weapon—may take Fire Breather Talent at half cost (Survival Guide p. 102).",
