      "customOneOffs": [
        "+1 to Spell Strength if a spell caster.",
        "Bite double damage to Nightlords and Nightlands denizens.",
        "Fire Breather Talent (if taken) double damage vs Nightlords/Nightlands.",
        "Flying speed 1D4x10+88 mph (70–90 mph); wings 1D6x10+60 S.D.C. each, regrow in one day if destroyed.",
